text: bhai maddheshiya, woh jo 4 din bina soye antaragni'19 me kaam kare the as a manager, bhai tu sath tha to kaafi easy ho gaya tha manage karna. bhai hall me cricket bhi bahut khele hai tere sath, yr bas wo H3PL me 1 run nahi bana tha ek over me uska gam reh gaya. bhai 7th sem me bhi kaafi risk liya tha tune, guts chayiye uske liye lekin last me phod diya. bhai ese hi mehnat karte raaho aur phod dena is baar placement me, phir din raat maje karege college me apan. All the best.
author: Suhail  Khan

text:
Bhai kele, bhale hi me dusre wing ka tha lekin tumhare room me hi pura maze karne aata tha pure first year me. bhai jo call aata tha tera MM ke liye aaja sherkhan phir pure 10-12 log tere room me ho jate the aur sabse jada tu hi chillata tha especially mujh par. apni ladai bhi kafi hue hai choti choti baat pe lekin maza bhi bahut aaya hai tere sath. bhai woh mukhteshwar wala trip hamesha yaad rahega jo zostel me maze kare the tum logo ke sath.
Ese hi muskurate rehna aur chaapte rehna, aur jaldi se UPSC bhi crack kar lena and congrats for cracking IIMA, IIMB and all the best for your future,
author: Suhail  Khan

text: Bhai Jatin, bahut mast banda hai bhai tu, honest, humble aur sab ko hasata rehta hai. Pura first year hi tere room me MM khelte hue nikala hai. bhai 2nd year ki trip bhi yaadgar thi, bahut maza aaya tum logo ke sath. bhai apna bhaiyo ka group bahut backchod hai, apni wing se jada tumhare sath maza aaya. bhai contact me rehna hamesha aur jab bhi plan banao bhaiyo ke sath bhulna nahi hame. you can always count me in. All the best.
author: Suhail  Khan

text: Bhai Ramji known you from 2nd year techkriti, phir to sath me manager bhi ban gaye antaragni me. woh 4 din jo Antaragni'19 me jo kaam kara tha bina soye wo hamesha yaad rahega. bahut bakchodi kaati thi us time aur chalo last me akhir kar Shankar Mahadevan ko tum hi leke aaye the. bhai mast aadmi ho tum, kaafi maza aaya tumhare sath kaam karke. All the best.
author: Suhail  Khan

text: Bhai sachin tumhare pass hi aata tha me har baar assignment ke liye, bahut help kare ho be. acha hua tum branch change kar liye. tumhare bharose hi chod deta tha har cheez. Mujhe to tum loner nahi lagte, itna to mil jul ke rehte the sab ke sath. roote roote intern lagwa liye pata bhi nahi chala aur phir PPO. chalo intern ka party to de diya tha tune. pagalo ki tarah nachte ho bhai pura video rakha hai tumhara. hopefully phir milna hoga kabhi aur ese hi tarakki karte rehna. All the best.
author: Suhail  Khan

text: Bhai shashi bahut maze kare hai bhai sath me. Woh roz raat ko badminton khelna, Ipl ke time team banana, players ko galiyana aur tumhari hawabaji sunnaðŸ˜‚, weekend me Z square aur movie to fix hi tha. Raat ko ese hi campus ke bahar raj aur bihari ke sath cycling pe jana aur woh amritsar ka tour. Manali wale me kaat ke ghar chale gaye the, woh yaad rahega mujheðŸ˜›, hopefully aur achi jagah chalege. Bhai tumne pura balance banake rakha, enjoy bhi bahut kara ham logo ke sath aur academics me bhi chaapa. bas final year ka enjoyment reh gaya apna. Hopefully phirse milna hoga kabhiðŸ™‚ and All the best for your future.
author: Suhail  Khan

text: Aur skand baba, bahut mast aadmi ho tum, hamesha muskurate rehte ho, bhai exam ke ek din phele padh ke podna kaise hai koi tumse seekhe. Pura prime ke sare ache series dhek dale tumne aur phir aate the batane hame. badmiton khelne me bhi kaafi maza aaya tumhare sath. bhai khane ke liye bahut puntual the tum, hamesha exact 12:30 aur 7:30 pe bahar aate the aur phele shashi aur phir hamare room me ghuste the. bhai tumhare alag jalwa tha day 1 intern. chalo party wagera bhi de diye tum. bhai ese hi haste rehna, all the best, milte hai kabhi.
author: Suhail  Khan

text: Aur bhai ujjwal, baski champ, DR1 aur kya kya bolu tere bare me. bhai mast banda hai tu, always sincere towards studies aur sath me baski ko time dena, bhai you are allrounder. BC jo manali trip me tu chutiya kaat ke chala gaya tha, aur phir naya uzzwal ko le jana pada tha. Chalo bhai ek trip to ho gaya sath me, alag level ka maza aaya usme to. Ek saal aur hai apne pass, ek aur bada plan banayege placement ke baad, tab tak mast padte hai, all the best.
author: Suhail  Khan

text: Utsav bro, bahut mast banda hai tu, always smiling, humble aur hamesha chill rehta hai. kaafi help kara hai bhai tu department ke courses me. tere hi assignments wagera chaapa karte the ham log. bhai woh 3rd year me jo bakchodi kari hai pandit ke room me, wo to yaad rahega hamesha. All the best bhai aur ese hi muskurate rehna.
author: Suhail  Khan

text: Bhai yogi, apne department ka sabse mast banda hai tu, always making everybody laugh. Bhai che352 me to alag level pe bakchodi kaati thi tere room pe.
author: Suhail  Khan
